thread.title_full: OCEANE Body.Mind.Soul reviewed by Kylie Cunningham

author: Kylie Cunningham
title: Kylie Cunningham
text: My order was received super quick (to Australia) and I was surprised with a complimentary hand & body cream too. Great communication throughout my purchase. Love their white pearl exfoliating gel. A must in your weekly skincare regime!
